{"tid":140487,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"微型電腦Raspberry Pi Zero W　10美元有交易","createTime":"2017-03-02T08:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T13:03:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4742a72647565b85bb8e338316a9a23d9ffc15b3","tid":140487,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170302/large/55ss10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170302%2Flarge%2F55ss10.jpg&h=03904498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10美元（約$78)一部電腦？有冇咁誇張？其實剛剛面世的Raspberry Pi Zero W已經比只賣5美元的上一代Raspberry Pi Zero貴上一倍！可能同大家想像中的電腦有唔同，具體地講Zero W其實是一塊小型主機板，主要用作開發及DIY設計小型裝置，但當中已加入1GHz處理器、512MB RAM、Mini-HDMI輸出、Micro-USB On-The-Go介面、Micro-USB電源介面及40-pin針頭等等，可以自行接上輸入裝置及顯示器使用。但點解會比上代貴一倍咁多，主要原因是Zero W追加802.11n無線網絡加Bluetooth4.0，自行搞DIY Project時彈性會更大。如果想外形更好睇的話，還可另購特製Zero W膠殼，會附送3種不同面蓋，適合不同情況需要。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170302/large/55ss11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170302%2Flarge%2F55ss11.jpg&h=cf3a4406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 嫌主機板外觀唔吸引，亦可另購特製膠殼使用。 <br />\n <br />\n資料來源：Raspberry Pi Foundation<br />\n <br />\n文：布偉倫<br />\n <br />\n2017果籽繼續認真知味。識買惜用。行以求知。好事多為。重修舊好。<br />\n緊貼果籽報道，即like：<a href=\"http://fb.me/AS.AppleDaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2FAS.AppleDaily&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=26392505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/AS.AppleDaily</a>"},{"pid":"d48fd34b603403b5770844d00f24c39a2960757d","tid":140487,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052664226c446